            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para comenzar a agrupar código relacionado, empezamos codificando la palabra clave <code>func</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"4\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>func</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Function name",
            "id": 127087,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A continuación viene el nombre de la función en camel case, como <code>greetUser</code>, seguido de paréntesis, <code>(</code> y <code>)</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"5\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>greetUser</code> seguido de <code>(</code> y finalmente <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Braces",
            "id": 127088,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Las llaves <code>{</code> y <code>}</code> delimitan el bloque de código que pertenece a la función.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>{</code> seguido de <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Between braces",
            "id": 127089,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>El código que queremos agrupar va entre las llaves. Esta función agrupa dos declaraciones <code>print()</code> relacionadas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>print</code> seguido de <code>(\"Welcome back\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Calling the function",
            "id": 127090,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para ejecutar el código, necesitamos <strong>llamar</strong> a la función. Hacemos eso escribiendo su nombre seguido de paréntesis, como <code>greetUser()</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greetUser()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"84\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Good morning Anna\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Welcome back\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>greetUser()</code>.</p></body></html>"
